data.message: Must be my favorite, but now I'm a bit older and see your lyrics for what they were.. a way to push off those mofos.. but  your holding on to the past shady... tell us about the government, news,deception, laws, educate,health,and the youth that looks up to you,dont  brain wash another generation of lost souls. ..  your still my # one lyricist!! but turn that water into wine once in a while.. instead of sour grapes .
